  "texts": [
    "The best results are obtained for C hyper-parameter equal to 0.0015 for this dataset, resulting in a feature subset consisting of only seven features.",
    "It is important to note that 100% result for LOSO CV does not mean that the proposed system can correctly classify all samples of the dataset.",
    "Because a subject is classified as PD if more than half of its samples are predicted as 1, otherwise the subject is classified as healthy.",
    "Thus, it is expected that for any disease having more than one sample per patient, the proposed system could be an ideal candidate for diagnosis.",
    "Moreover, optimal subset of features for C = 0.0015 and with n = 7 contains F 5, F 10, F 15, F 19, F 21, F 24 and F 26."
  ],
